      <h2 class="uc-section-title">Button</h2>
      <p>You can create a buttons by specifying the <code>uc-btn</code> class.</p>

      <div class="doc-component-box" id="c-1">
        <h3>1. Basic</h3>
        <p>Create a basic button.</p>

        <div class="doc-component-preview">
          <div class="uc-content">
            <div class="uc-btn"><a href="#">Button</a></div>
            <button class="uc-btn"><span>Button</span></button>
            <div class="uc-btn"><span>Button</span></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="uc-code-unit">
<pre><code class="html">&lt;div class="uc-btn"&gt;&lt;a href="#"&gt;Button&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;button class="uc-btn"&gt;&lt;span&gt;Button&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/button&gt;
&lt;!-- It can be used in `a` tag. --&gt;
&lt;div class="uc-btn"&gt;&lt;span&gt;Button&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
</code></pre>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="doc-component-box" id="c-2">
        <h3>2. Color variations</h3>
        <p>There are abundant color variations.</p>

        <div class="doc-component-preview">
          <div><div class="uc-btn _ghost"><a href="#">Ghost</a></div></div>
          <div>&nbsp;</div>
          <div><div class="uc-btn _primary"><a href="#">Primary</a></div></div>
          <div>&nbsp;</div>
          <div><div class="uc-btn _secondary"><a href="">Secondary</a></div></div>
          <div>&nbsp;</div>
          <div><div class="uc-btn _success"><a href="">Success</a></div></div>
          <div>&nbsp;</div>
          <div><div class="uc-btn _danger"><a href="">Danger</a></div></div>
          <div>&nbsp;</div>
